Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.09,0:01:34.99,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Teppei!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.90,0:01:38.79,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,The Earth Engine Impacter...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.19,0:03:24.39,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.35,0:03:30.27,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,The Kiltgang has broken through defensive zone 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.27,0:03:32.06,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,About to make contact with Earth Engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.32,0:03:37.61,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I've found a new feast...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.28,0:03:49.80,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear me, Earth Driver?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.26,0:03:51.37,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,U-Uncle?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.37,0:03:52.25,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Daichi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.86,0:03:54.90,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Daichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.96,0:03:57.92,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.50,0:03:59.76,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.63,0:04:05.51,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The consultation system isn't working yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.85,0:04:07.98,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We can't assist the Earth Engine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.98,0:04:09.39,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Daichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.39,0:04:10.31,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.31,0:04:10.72,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Daichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.14,0:04:13.34,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,This is Peter Westvillage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.34,0:04:15.23,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Code Papillon, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.46,0:04:18.26,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,This is Code Papillon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.26,0:04:19.69,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,I'm aware of the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.17,0:04:21.18,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.18,0:04:22.15,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.15,0:04:23.68,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,Impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.33,0:04:27.37,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I request your help with flight \Ndirection for the Earth Engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.71,0:04:28.78,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.78,0:04:30.95,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,I'll borrow your communication line.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.74,0:04:34.99,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,Earth Driver, you can hear me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.99,0:04:35.54,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.54,0:04:36.82,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.82,0:04:38.63,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a magical girl who's on your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.21,0:04:42.68,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, you're on a battlefield. \NDo you understand that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.68,0:04:44.84,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if I understand it or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.06,0:04:48.51,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.59,0:04:53.57,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,I know that if the thing in front \Nof me reaches Earth, it'll be bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.57,0:04:54.52,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,That's good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.19,0:04:58.78,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,The Earth Engine is currently filled \Nwith the power of Livlaster...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.78,0:05:01.53,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,That is, your life energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.14,0:05:04.25,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,You can pilot it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.81,0:05:05.49,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.91,0:05:10.25,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... Then how did you get up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.25,0:05:11.93,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,Was the gun controlling you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.93,0:05:13.11,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.21,0:05:17.39,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,It's my own will telling me I must defeat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.80,0:05:20.09,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,I believe the gun only helped me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.48,0:05:22.00,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what are you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.00,0:05:23.38,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Just a high school kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.38,0:05:24.30,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.87,0:05:27.98,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, I'll take control.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.98,0:05:29.89,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,You can provide the power.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.89,0:05:32.25,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,Grip the Livlaster tightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.85,0:05:39.61,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,You stopped moving all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.61,0:05:41.57,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Are you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.53,0:05:55.54,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,You're too slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.90,0:06:07.13,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hit her...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.58,0:06:11.80,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's hard without direct control.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.63,0:06:13.97,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,If you die, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.73,0:06:19.79,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.85,0:06:24.92,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Die? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.10,0:06:29.14,Default - flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,If your dad ever dies...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.34,0:06:32.49,Default - flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,He'll die with a smile on his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.54,0:06:35.69,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.13,0:06:37.23,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.95,0:06:41.17,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,I just need to hit it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.17,0:06:43.46,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.00,0:06:51.59,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,That light...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.64,0:06:54.26,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Orgone energy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.39,0:07:01.10,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.53,0:07:07.40,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.40,0:07:08.11,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,I hit her!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.11,0:07:09.32,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the issue!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.09,0:07:30.54,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,I hit her...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.54,0:07:33.73,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,You're interesting. I like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.26,0:07:41.25,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Kiltgang interception successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.25,0:07:42.73,Default,Yo,0000,0000,0000,,What an ugly fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.14,0:07:45.69,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,But we won.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.83,0:07:48.90,Default,Yo,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.95,0:07:54.41,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Code Papillon, thank you for your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.76,0:07:57.42,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,It was the Earth Driver that did all the work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.42,0:07:59.72,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,It was fun, Globe-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.62,0:08:03.62,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I know I acted without consulting you,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.62,0:08:07.32,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,but given the urgency of the situation, \NI hope you'll forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.32,0:08:11.47,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,In my experience, she is the \Nonly flight director capable
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.97,0:08:15.17,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,of assisting the Earth Engine in that situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.60,0:08:16.96,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Who is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.96,0:08:20.56,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Someone I was thinking of \Nbringing to the base soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.91,0:08:23.20,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you the documents later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.75,0:08:29.36,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It's clearly different than the \None we saw nine years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.46,0:08:34.49,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It seems the active phase of the Kiltgang\Nthat we feared has begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.49,0:08:38.93,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I've raised all satellite bases to DEFCON 1,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.93,0:08:42.96,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,and all Impacters in defensive zones \Nwill be ready at a moment's notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.33,0:08:46.08,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,That aside...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.89,0:08:53.38,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I hadn't heard anything about the Earth Driver \Nbeing stationed at Tanegashima already.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.09,0:08:55.59,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.86,0:09:02.22,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Earth Engine has activated feathering system.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.22,0:09:06.02,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Set to return to Tanegashima on autopilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.70,0:09:08.43,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,This is Salty Dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.43,0:09:10.56,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The area around the airport is cordoned off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.56,0:09:12.11,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Begin operation immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.63,0:09:15.35,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,This is Tanegashima HQ. Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.11,0:09:40.30,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,So you're the Earth Driver, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.64,0:09:50.15,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,The Name of the Gun Is Livlaster
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.59,0:09:59.82,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see any physical abnormalities.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.42,0:10:02.49,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Not at the moment, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.24,0:10:26.12,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It seems a second Livlaster has appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.79,0:10:31.86,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You said nothing to us of this possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.61,0:10:35.69,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You said nothing to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.76,0:10:38.02,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.02,0:10:40.99,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have plenty of time to discuss it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.52,0:10:42.91,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like your fever's down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.48,0:10:46.12,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to talk to you, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.55,0:10:51.33,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,About that rainbow you were \Nprobably responsible for...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.40,0:10:56.86,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,On the outside, Globe is an \Ninternational organization
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.86,0:11:00.26,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,devoted to space development \Nfor peaceful purposes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.42,0:11:05.72,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,But in truth, it is a defensive organization \Nhere to fight those alien invaders.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.35,0:11:08.49,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, this is a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.49,0:11:10.54,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Then when my dad died...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.54,0:11:12.99,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't an accident, after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.51,0:11:17.44,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you get that gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.33,0:11:20.83,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.83,0:11:23.41,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,All of a sudden, I was holding it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.91,0:11:25.99,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,This toy isn't a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.59,0:11:27.51,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You can have it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.71,0:11:37.69,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Those two...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.19,0:11:39.20,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.84,0:11:44.76,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Who gave you permission \Nto use the lead gears?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.88,0:11:46.76,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.76,0:11:49.16,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Of course we're using them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.16,0:11:52.89,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,If they were all as quiet and obedient \Nas she is, it wouldn't be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.25,0:11:57.11,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,But some of them use their \Nsingularities without warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.11,0:11:58.02,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Teppei!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.40,0:12:00.53,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,You're Teppei, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.72,0:12:02.73,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Daichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.22,0:12:04.40,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.40,0:12:06.28,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't she the girl
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.70,0:12:08.84,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,we saw back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.54,0:12:15.22,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Is he the boy who was \Nthere when Hana awoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.22,0:12:18.11,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Did I not forbid the use of the lead gears?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.11,0:12:22.01,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Salty Dog does not only inspect Globe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.54,0:12:23.01,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,I got even better at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.01,0:12:23.93,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}We are also its internal police force.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.01,0:12:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... Daichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.93,0:12:25.14,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You're exceeding your authority!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.14,0:12:28.81,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}In an emergency, I am authorized to \Ntake any steps I deem necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.57,0:12:27.80,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep the promise I made that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.33,0:12:28.81,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.18,0:12:29.98,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You, too, Teppei!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.98,0:12:30.47,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Daichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.89,0:12:43.49,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.92,0:12:50.24,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.85,0:12:51.87,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,What are these things?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.44,0:12:54.00,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.59,0:13:04.43,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let that animal out of its cage!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.77,0:13:17.65,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry about earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.33,0:13:19.61,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It hurt, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.47,0:13:24.82,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make sure those people \Nnever touch you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.79,0:13:33.35,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think he fired the gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.35,0:13:35.54,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I think the gun made him fire it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.59,0:13:39.75,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I believe Livlaster, that energy generator,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.28,0:13:43.32,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,is more like an extra-dimensional life form
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.32,0:13:47.03,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,in the shape of a gun than an actual gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.48,0:13:49.55,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it has a will.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.55,0:13:52.76,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,And that will activated the Earth Engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.27,0:13:55.27,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,That's the obvious conclusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.80,0:14:02.36,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, the Livlaster used \Nhim to activate the Earth Engine?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.40,0:14:05.65,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Then, once the investigation ends,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.65,0:14:07.82,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,we have him swear an oath of secrecy,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.82,0:14:09.57,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,and send him back to the mainland?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.95,0:14:20.04,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Now that the Kiltgang's active phase has \Nbegun, can we get away with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.60,0:14:27.26,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Technology and Research Division 3 is \Ncomplaining that they can't set a schedule
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.73,0:14:30.97,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,for the Machine Goodfellow \Ndemonstration experiments.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.40,0:14:33.40,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.43,0:14:40.15,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Why are they letting the designer children \Ndetermine the development schedule?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.37,0:14:43.13,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,That's my policy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.69,0:14:44.77,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Something wrong with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.81,0:14:50.67,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't allowing them too much freedom dangerous?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.78,0:14:53.58,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What about the Ego Block?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.06,0:14:56.77,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine... It was unharmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.77,0:14:59.46,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,In Ego Block form,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.46,0:15:02.58,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,we can use the Entangle Link \Nto travel through hyperspace.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.99,0:15:07.31,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,But if we materialize in Ego Block \Nform too close to Earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.31,0:15:09.30,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,it causes a libido burst.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.08,0:15:11.76,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Final approach must be
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.76,0:15:15.60,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,through normal space via the Kiltgang.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.35,0:15:18.97,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,If they knew how this worked
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.97,0:15:23.23,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,when they designed their defense system, \Nthey can't be underestimated.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.23,0:15:27.58,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Life never goes the way you \Nthink it should, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.86,0:15:35.94,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,So, what was the Impacter that \Nshot down the Malkin like?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.78,0:15:47.46,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,A manned Impacter, using a Livlaster?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.63,0:15:52.43,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm told letting them do what they want
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.90,0:15:57.43,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,is the most efficient way to develop \Nthe Machine Goodfellows.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.06,0:15:59.33,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Told?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.01,0:16:02.08,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,By whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.85,0:16:20.83,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening, CEO Kube.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.83,0:16:23.74,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Something seems to have happened \Naboard the {\i1}Tenkaidou{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.98,0:16:27.80,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm impressed you're aware of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.80,0:16:29.34,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Very impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.10,0:16:31.84,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Stop talking like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.81,0:16:34.51,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You don't like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.51,0:16:37.02,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's really cool and computer-y.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.15,0:16:41.85,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Your secretary, Hitomi-chan, was wearing \Na very attractive suit today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.20,0:16:44.39,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You should ask her on a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.39,0:16:49.61,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The Kiltgang won't reach Earth sooner \Nthan anticipated, will they?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.14,0:16:53.03,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,My simulation's predictions are perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.03,0:16:56.04,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Globe will buy the required time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.63,0:17:01.00,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,And if you'd gone for it, you could \Neasily have had Hitomi-chan tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.42,0:17:03.58,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,She was totally up for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.11,0:17:06.08,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Humanity will survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.57,0:17:08.17,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The chosen humanity...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.66,0:17:12.21,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,No, the humanity I choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.70,0:17:16.13,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What is the Macbeth Revolution's \Npresent likelihood of success?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.03,0:17:18.84,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,One hundred percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.84,0:17:20.15,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You're certain?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.73,0:17:22.73,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Puck doesn't lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.49,0:17:26.97,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse to accept this method!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.97,0:17:28.44,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,He's still a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.76,0:17:32.61,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I can't have him behaving as he did yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.26,0:17:34.78,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Science Chief, do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.56,0:17:41.04,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Daichi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.02,0:17:44.83,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I saw you yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.37,0:17:52.20,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm this base's science chief, Peter Westvillage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.63,0:17:55.85,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Today, we'll be discussing the Livlaster,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.85,0:17:57.72,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,so I had these two accompany me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.23,0:18:00.91,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What's that girl's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.42,0:18:03.19,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,That is none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.19,0:18:07.35,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,There are many things in this world \Nthat you don't need to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.69,0:18:10.42,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,That's kind of exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.95,0:18:15.28,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The gun you had is the second of its kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.74,0:18:20.62,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We believed the Livlaster you \Nhad to be a type of weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.26,0:18:23.82,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,But its bearer, this girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.82,0:18:25.70,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hana Mutou cannot fire it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.59,0:18:30.96,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,So we trained this boy, Teppei Arashi, instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.65,0:18:32.88,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hana Mutou...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.71,0:18:34.87,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Your name's Hana!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.55,0:18:38.51,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Science Chief, you're talking too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.51,0:18:39.38,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.04,0:18:44.14,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,He'll be working with us on this plan for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.14,0:18:49.69,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you plan to take \Nthese two yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.51,0:18:53.23,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.73,0:18:56.23,Default - flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Come out of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.56,0:18:58.49,Default - flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you my boomerang.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.72,0:19:02.94,Default - flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Boomerang?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.74,0:19:07.12,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to show them my boomerang.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.50,0:19:08.54,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Your boomerang?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.01,0:19:10.42,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Long ago, I promised her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.35,0:19:12.83,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Promised...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.72,0:19:15.47,Default - italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Then he's just an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.18,0:19:19.55,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Why were they suddenly in \Nso much pain yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.12,0:19:22.30,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,They are under our protection and observation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.92,0:19:27.18,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,As a necessary safety precaution, \Nthey wear lead gears on their heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.59,0:19:30.27,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,If they try to leave the base's quarantine zone,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.27,0:19:35.06,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,that sensor tower will detect it \Nand inflict a minor degree of pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.13,0:19:38.19,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Did they do something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.20,0:19:42.08,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,That isn't it, but they're dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.87,0:19:45.43,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,They have a special power...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.96,0:19:50.15,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,And that means you'll be wearing \None starting today, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.96,0:19:56.11,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I've sent a request to HQ for permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.66,0:20:01.51,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to investigate why you \Nwere able to fire the Livlaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.47,0:20:06.99,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Just be grateful you survived \Nfiring that gun's first shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.43,0:20:11.10,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't feel like that kind of thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.54,0:20:15.34,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where is my Livlaster?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.34,0:20:18.36,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to have the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.36,0:20:23.15,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,There is no such thing as "your" Livlaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.15,0:20:24.77,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We're done here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.26,0:20:26.62,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Teppei... Hana.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.19,0:20:30.44,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wait at the coast.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.32,0:20:36.58,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Daichi Manatsu is Taiyou Manatsu's son.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.25,0:20:41.80,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,His father came up with the name "Earth Engine."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.34,0:20:44.97,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The power of a captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.10,0:20:51.76,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow, it feels like fate that \Nhe boarded the Earth Engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.16,0:20:58.52,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Is it out of character for me to speak of fate?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.77,0:21:00.97,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.97,0:21:04.28,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Daichi Manatsu's lead gear has \Ngone into warning mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.95,0:21:11.58,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,This is rough...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.89,0:21:22.22,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,There's a strong Orgone signal \Nfrom the Livlaster in storage!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.22,0:21:23.09,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.54,0:21:24.75,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We're losing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.08,0:21:38.86,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.06,0:21:42.61,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hana?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.08,0:21:49.87,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Come here, Pitz.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.54,0:21:59.83,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You think you're going outside, Hana?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.83,0:22:01.13,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.67,0:22:08.63,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,But I want to see the boomerang!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.76,0:22:13.77,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The boomerang?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.92,0:22:17.71,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.96,0:22:26.44,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Got it...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.53,0:22:31.07,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why did you come back to this island, Daichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.02,0:22:33.18,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.18,0:22:35.04,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I came to fulfill my promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.26,0:22:38.71,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I remembered...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.56,0:22:43.00,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,How good the wind on this island feels...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.80,0:24:16.10,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be living with Uncle Nishikubo...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.10,0:24:18.10,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, the commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.10,0:24:22.85,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be Teppei and me, and Hana and Akari.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.35,0:24:26.77,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,But the Kiltgang attacks again!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.77,0:24:29.44,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,And because of Salty Dog's plot,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.44,0:24:32.61,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I launch in a malfunctioning Earth Engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.24,0:24:35.32,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, on episode 3 of {\i1}Captain Earth{\i0}:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.63,0:24:36.99,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,The Rainbow of Albion.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.63,0:24:36.99,Title2,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,The Rainbow of Albion
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.99,0:24:39.16,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,Earth Engine, expand!
